snippet.title: ZUMBA® BURN IT UP! Coming to Nintendo Switch November 22nd
snippet.description:
Everyone’s favorite dance party is back! Dance anytime, anywhere with ZUMBA® BURN IT UP! coming to Nintendo Switch on November 22nd. Zumba® is a global movement that brings the fun to fitness with over 15 million people taking weekly classes across 186 countries. Get your fix of the Zumba® program anytime, anywhere with high-energy routines and hip-shaking jams including chart-topping hits and Zumba originals. Use the Joy-Con controllers to track your movements and get rewarded for dancing with energy and flair. Visit  www.zumbagame.com to pre-order now.

Join us on social media: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/zumba/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/zumba
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/zumba
Discord: https://www.discord.gg/Zumba
